Presentation Setup
Create engaging academic presentations by following three quick steps:

Save the slide template below as slides/presentation.qmd.
Render it with quarto render slides/presentation.qmd to produce slides/presentation.html.
Embed the rendered HTML so readers can page through the deck inline.

::: {.ratio ratio-16x9 .slides-preview}  :::

